<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/361100-do-i-need-to-read-the-angel-s-game-before">Do I need to read The Angel&#39;s Game before I can read this one? It seems like this is a continuation of Daniel&#39;s story from The Shadow of the Wind, while The Angel&#39;s Game is a completely separate story and character. While I be confused if I skip The Angel&#39;s Game and go straight onto The Prisoner of Heaven?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_361100'><a id="like_count_community_question_361100" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/361100?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13623012-the-prisoner-of-heaven">like</a></span>

</li>
