<li class='cover' id='bookCover_59076506'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59076506-labrynth-of-the-spirits"><img alt="Labrynth of the Spirits" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
